name: 9Shot
summary: This game is purely for catharsis; there's no main storyline and it will never conclude "9Shot" is a first-person shooter game set in a zombie-infested Tokyo streets. Your objective is simple: survive against waves of zombies for as long as possible. Earn points by killing zombies to upgrade weapons
